Input file (geometry): dia.xyz
Input file (parameters): tightbind.parms.NRL_TB.C.xml

eval:
  evaluate energy, force, virial
  relax w.r.t. forces, virial

Example run
  ../../build.${QUIP_ARCH}/eval E F relax init_args='{TB NRL-TB}' param_file=tightbind.parms.NRL_TB.C.xml < dia.xyz 
For brief usage message, do:
  ../../build.${QUIP_ARCH}/eval
